SNP_TRT : LKM Oracle to Oracle (DB Link)

COMPONENT NAME: LKM Oracle to Oracle Push (DB Link) COMPONENT VERSION: 12.1.2.0.0 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.2.0.0 or above
DESCRIPTION:
In the source database, push data into target over an Oracle database link.
Database link name for accessing target database
Enter the name of the database link. If not set a default name will be used.
Prepare: drop database link to target

<?
String dblinkToTgt = "$[dbLinkName]";
if ("".equals(dblinkToTgt)) {
  dblinkToTgt = odiRef.getInfo("DEST_LSCHEMA_NAME");
}
if ("TRUE".equals("$[isConcurrent]")) {
  dblinkToTgt += "%UNIQUE_SESSION_TAG";
}
dblinkToTgt = dblinkToTgt.replaceAll(" ","");
dblinkToTgt = dblinkToTgt.replaceAll("-","");
dblinkToTgt = odiRef.getFormattedName(dblinkToTgt);
?>
drop database link <?=dblinkToTgt ?>

<?
String dblinkToTgt = "$[dbLinkName]";
if ("".equals(dblinkToTgt)) {
  dblinkToTgt = odiRef.getInfo("DEST_LSCHEMA_NAME");
}
if ("TRUE".equals("$[isConcurrent]")) {
  dblinkToTgt += "%UNIQUE_SESSION_TAG";
}
dblinkToTgt = dblinkToTgt.replaceAll(" ","");
dblinkToTgt = dblinkToTgt.replaceAll("-","");
dblinkToTgt = odiRef.getFormattedName(dblinkToTgt);
String tgtUserName = odiRef.getInfo("DEST_USER_NAME");
String tgtServerInstance = odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DSERV_NAME");
String tgtSID = "";
if (tgtServerInstance != null && tgtServerInstance.trim().length() != 0) {
  tgtSID = tgtServerInstance;
} else {
  String tgtJDBCURL = odiRef.getInfo("DEST_JAVA_URL");
  if (tgtJDBCURL != null && tgtJDBCURL.trim().length() != 0) {
    tgtSID = tgtJDBCURL.substring(tgtJDBCURL.lastIndexOf("@") + 1);
    tgtSID = tgtSID.substring(tgtSID.lastIndexOf(":") + 1);
    if (tgtSID.lastIndexOf("/") >= 0){
      tgtSID = tgtSID.substring(tgtSID.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
    }
  }
}
tgtSID = tgtSID.trim();
if (tgtSID.length() == 0) {
  throw new OdiKMException("Failed calculating target SID.");
}
?>
create database link <?=dblinkToTgt ?> connect to <?=tgtUserName ?> identified by <@=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_PASS") @> using '<?=tgtSID ?>'
